statements: SELECT * FROM website_traffic_data;
SELECT visitor_id, page_visited FROM website_traffic_data WHERE visit_duration_minutes > 10;
SELECT * FROM website_traffic_data WHERE entry_timestamp < '2022-01-01';
SELECT page_visited, visit_duration_minutes FROM website_traffic_data WHERE exit_timestamp IS NULL;
SELECT visitor_id, entry_timestamp, exit_timestamp FROM website_traffic_data ORDER BY entry_timestamp DESC, exit_timestamp ASC LIMIT 5;
SELECT visitor_id, page_visited, visit_duration_minutes, entry_timestamp, exit_timestamp FROM website_traffic_data ORDER BY visitor_id DESC, entry_timestamp ASC LIMIT 10
SELECT page_visited, visit_duration_minutes FROM website_traffic_data WHERE visit_duration_minutes > 5 AND page_visited LIKE '%homepage%'
SELECT visitor_id, page_visited, exit_timestamp FROM website_traffic_data WHERE entry_timestamp >= '2022-01-01 00:00:00' AND exit_timestamp < '2022-02-01 00:00:00'
SELECT visitor_id, COUNT(*) AS visit_count FROM website_traffic_data GROUP BY visitor_id HAVING visit_count > 1 ORDER BY visit_count DESC
SELECT MAX(visit_duration_minutes) AS longest_visit_duration FROM website_traffic_data WHERE page_visited = 'blog'
SELECT * FROM website_traffic_data ORDER BY visit_time DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT page_url, visitor_id FROM website_traffic_data WHERE traffic_source='Organic';
SELECT id, page_url, visit_time FROM website_traffic_data WHERE id > 100 AND visitor_id = 2500;
SELECT * FROM marketing_strategies WHERE assigned_budget > 50000 ORDER BY strategy_id;
SELECT strategy_name, conversion_rate FROM marketing_strategies WHERE target_audience='Millennials';
SELECT * FROM website_traffic_data ORDER BY visit_time DESC, visitor_id ASC LIMIT 10;
SELECT page_url, visitor_id, COUNT(*) AS visit_count FROM website_traffic_data GROUP BY page_url, visitor_id HAVING visit_count > 2;
SELECT page_url, visit_time, traffic_source FROM website_traffic_data WHERE traffic_source = 'Organic' OR traffic_source = 'Referral' ORDER BY visit_time ASC LIMIT 5;
SELECT strategy_name, target_audience, conversion_rate FROM marketing_strategies WHERE conversion_rate >= 0.5 ORDER BY conversion_rate DESC;

SELECT * FROM website_traffic_data INNER JOIN marketing_strategies ON website_traffic_data.visitor_id = marketing_strategies.strategy_id WHERE website_traffic_data.visit_time >= '2022-01-01' AND marketing_strategies.assigned_budget >= 5000 ORDER BY website_traffic_data.visit_time ASC LIMIT 3;
SELECT * FROM website_traffic_data;
SELECT page_url, visited_at FROM website_traffic_data ORDER BY visited_at DESC;
SELECT source_name, source_type FROM traffic_sources WHERE source_type = 'Organic';
SELECT SUM(time_spent_on_page) AS total_time_spent FROM user_engagement;
SELECT page_url, interaction_count FROM website_traffic_data JOIN user_engagement ON website_traffic_data.visitor_id = user_engagement.visitor_id ORDER BY interaction_count DESC;
SELECT * FROM website_traffic_data WHERE page_url LIKE '%homepage%' ORDER BY visited_at DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT page_url, visited_at FROM website_traffic_data WHERE visited_at BETWEEN '2021-01-01' AND '2021-06-30' ORDER BY visited_at ASC;
SELECT visitor_id, COUNT(*) AS visits FROM website_traffic_data GROUP BY visitor_id HAVING COUNT(*) > 5 ORDER BY visits DESC;
SELECT w.page_url, t.source_name FROM website_traffic_data w JOIN traffic_sources t ON w.page_url = t.source_name WHERE w.visited_at > '2021-07-01';
SELECT w.page_url, u.time_spent_on_page FROM website_traffic_data w JOIN user_engagement u ON w.visitor_id = u.visitor_id ORDER BY u.time_spent_on_page DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT * FROM website_traffic_data;
SELECT page_url, traffic_source FROM website_traffic_data ORDER BY visit_timestamp DESC;
SELECT user_name, age, gender FROM user_demographics WHERE location = 'New York';
SELECT campaign_name, budget FROM marketing_campaigns WHERE start_date >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT click_id, user_id, page_url, clicked_timestamp FROM clickstream_data ORDER BY clicked_timestamp ASC;
SELECT * FROM website_traffic_data LIMIT 10;
SELECT page_url, traffic_source, visit_timestamp FROM website_traffic_data WHERE traffic_source = 'Organic' ORDER BY visit_timestamp DESC;
SELECT user_name, age, gender, location FROM user_demographics WHERE age >= 25 AND gender = 'Female';
SELECT page_url, clicked_timestamp FROM clickstream_data WHERE clicked_timestamp > '2022-01-01' ORDER BY clicked_timestamp ASC LIMIT 5;
SELECT campaign_id, campaign_name, start_date, end_date, budget FROM marketing_campaigns WHERE budget > 5000.00 ORDER BY start_date DESC;
SELECT * FROM website_visitors;
SELECT visitor_id, visit_date, website_page FROM website_visitors WHERE visitor_country='USA';
SELECT visit_date, COUNT(*) AS total_visits FROM website_visitors GROUP BY visit_date;
SELECT visitor_country, AVG(visit_duration_minutes) AS avg_duration FROM website_visitors GROUP BY visitor_country;
SELECT campaign_name, start_date, end_date FROM marketing_campaigns WHERE end_date > '2022-01-01';
SELECT * FROM website_visitors WHERE visitor_country = 'USA';
SELECT visitor_id, visit_date, visit_duration_minutes FROM website_visitors WHERE visit_duration_minutes > 30 ORDER BY visit_date DESC;
SELECT website_page, visit_count FROM page_views WHERE visit_date > '2022-01-01';
SELECT campaign_name, start_date, end_date FROM marketing_campaigns WHERE start_date < '2022-06-01' AND end_date > '2022-12-31';
